p.em: Below is a website that gives correct information and resources about the Coronavirus. In a time where there is so much hype and misinformation, this website gives great resources to make you aware of the dangers and preventative measures.
Precautions you can take are below.

li.em: Cover your mouth and nose with a tissue when coughing or sneezing.
Wash your hands often with soap and water for at least 20 seconds. -Use an alcohol-based hand sanitizer if no soap and water are available.
Avoid assumptions or stereotypes about who you think might be sick.
Make sure the school has a way to contact parent(s) if a student becomes ill at school.
